    "Query Validation.",
    "Prior to processing a query, we employ OpenAI's omni-moderation-latest foot_0 model for safeguarding against potentially harmful content and return appropriate error messages.",
    "We use the Semantic Scholar API (Kinney et al., 2023) for retrieval, specifically its endpoint for keyword search over paper abstracts, and our new endpoint for querying snippets from open-access papers.",
    "A query decomposer re-formulates the user query for each endpoint and retrieves up to 256 snippets and 20 abstracts.",
